        "content": "<p>I have these assumptions:<br>\n<strong>h</strong>: (∀ t ∈ F, x ∈ t) ∧ ∀ t ∈ G, x ∈ t<br>\n<strong>h2</strong>: m ∈ F → x ∈ m<br>\n<strong>h1B</strong>: m ∈ G<br>\n<strong>h3</strong>: ∀ t ∈ G, x ∈ t<br>\n<strong>h4</strong>: m ∈ G → x ∈ m<br>\n<strong>h5</strong>: x ∈ m</p>\n<p>Goal: m ∈ F</p>\n<p>Isnt the following a valid counterexample?</p>\n<p>F={A,B}</p>\n<p>G={C,D}</p>\n<p>x∈A,x∈B,x∈m</p>\n<p>m=C</p>\n<p>We have x∈A,x∈B,x∈C</p>\n<p>However C∉F</p>\n<p>I might misunderstand something here. This is part of the set theory game.</p>",
        "id": 456252950,
        "sender_full_name": "Gridiron Player",
        "timestamp": 1722735789
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It would be better if you make this into an <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mwe.html\">#mwe</a> (and see <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib/wiki/Code-in-backticks\">#backticks</a>) or if you link to the specific point in the game. But yes at a glance it looks like your goal is unprovable from those assumptions, I assume because you must have gone down the wrong path at some point earlier in the proof of whatever you had to prove originally</p>",
        "id": 456294212,
        "sender_full_name": "Luigi Massacci",
        "timestamp": 1722764865
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>You're right, you won't be able to prove <code>m ∈ F</code> from the assumptions you have. <br>\n What level of the set theory game are you working on?  If you got yourself into a situation in which you need to prove this goal, then you've probably made a mistake.</p>",
        "id": 456339831,
        "sender_full_name": "Dan Velleman",
        "timestamp": 1722785445
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"453098\">@Dan Velleman</span>  <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"466290\">@Luigi Massacci</span> <br>\nWhats up guys. Sorry for the late response. I am working on level 4 of the \"Family Intersection World\". Specifically, I have to proof that  ⋂(F∪G)=(⋂F)∩(⋂G).</p>\n<p>This is what I have so far, but obviously, I went way too far:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">apply</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Subset</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">antisymm</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">rewrite</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">mem_inter_iff</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">apply</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">And</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">intro</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">rewrite</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">mem_sInter</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">at</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">rewrite</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">mem_sInter</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">m</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h1</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">apply</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">m</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">rewrite</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">mem_union</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">apply</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Or</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">inl</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h1</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">rewrite</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">mem_sInter</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">at</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">rewrite</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">mem_sInter</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">m</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h1</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">apply</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">m</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">apply</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Or</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">inr</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h1</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">rewrite</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">mem_sInter</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">m</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h1</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">rewrite</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">mem_inter_iff</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">at</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">rewrite</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">mem_sInter</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">at</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">m</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∈</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∈</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">m</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">left</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">m</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">apply</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h2</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">cases'</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">with</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h1A</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h1B</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h1A</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">rewrite</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">mem_sInter</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">at</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">rewrite</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">mem_sInter</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">at</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">rewrite</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">mem_sInter</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">at</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">rewrite</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">mem_sInter</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">at</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">rewrite</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">mem_sInter</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">at</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h3</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">t</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∈</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">G</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∈</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">t</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">right</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h4</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">m</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∈</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">G</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∈</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">m</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h3</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">m</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h5</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∈</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">m</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h4</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h1B</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
